import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import axios from 'axios'; import './css/Ticket.css'; function Ticket() { const [matches, setMatches] = useState([]); const [selectedCountry, setSelectedCountry] = useState(''); useEffect(() => { axios.get('https://worldcupjson.net/matches') .then(response => { setMatches(response.data); }) .catch(error => { console.error('Error fetching matches:', error); }); }, []); const handleCountryChange = (event) => { setSelectedCountry(event.target.value); }; const filterMatches = (matches) => { if (!selectedCountry) return matches; return matches.filter(match => match.home_team_country.includes(selectedCountry) || match.away_team_country.includes(selectedCountry) ); }; return (
